title: United Kingdom Imports Intra Eu - Woven Fabrics,Tuft Textile, Lace & Tapestries
description: Imports Intra Eu - Woven Fabrics,Tuft Textile, Lace & Tapestries in the United Kingdom increased to 9.39 GBP Million in September from 6.19 GBP Million in August of 2022. Imports Intra Eu - Woven Fabrics,Tuft Textile, Lac in the United Kingdom averaged 11.03 GBP Million from 1996 until 2022, reaching an all time high of 17.98 GBP Million in November of 2001 and a record low of 3.60 GBP Million in April of 2020.
